  "about": {
    "title": "About",
    "p1": "Jain Knowledge Base is a structured search system for Jain agamas, scriptures and classical literature, offering an organised, accessible exploration layer. Its purpose is to bring ancient knowledge to scholars, sadhakas and seekers through modern technology.",
    "p2": "The system presents the dictionary, topic index, gathas and shastra references as an interlinked graph. By establishing relationships between every word, topic and source, it offers a fresh perspective on the depth of Jain literature.",
